---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy policy" description="Privacy policy of Resolve IT: what data we collect, why, and what your rights are.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
      <p>How Resolve IT handles your personal data.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>Our website address is: <a href="https://www.resolveit.nl">https://www.resolveit.nl</a>. For questions about this privacy policy you can contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@resolveit.nl">contact@resolveit.nl</a> or by phone on 0411 799 828.</p>

      <h2>Which personal data we collect and why</h2>

      <h3>Comments</h3>
      <p>When visitors leave comments on the site, we collect the data shown in the comment form, as well as the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent to help with spam detection. An anonymised string derived from your email address (also called a hash) may be shared with the Gravatar service to check whether you use it. The Gravatar privacy policy is available on their own website.</p>

      <h3>Media</h3>
      <p>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS). Visitors to the website can download and view any location data from images on the website.</p>

      <h3>Contact forms</h3>
      <p>When you provide data to us via a contact form (such as name, email address, phone number and your message), we use it solely to answer your question or request and to carry out our services. We do not share this data with third parties other than as necessary for our services.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>When you leave a comment, you can indicate whether your name, email address and website may be stored in a cookie. We do this for your convenience, so you don’t have to enter these details again. We keep these cookies for one year.</p>
      <p>If you log in, we place a few cookies to store your login details and screen display choices. Login cookies are kept for two days, screen display choices for one year. If you choose “Remember me”, your login is kept for two weeks. See our <a href="/en/cookiebeleid">cookie policy</a> for more information.</p>

      <h2>Embedded content from other websites</h2>
      <p>Posts on this site may contain embedded content (for example videos, images, posts). Embedded content from other websites behaves exactly as if the visitor had visited that other website. These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking and monitor your interaction with this embedded content.</p>

      <h2>How long we keep your data</h2>
      <p>If you leave a comment, that comment and its metadata are retained. This way we can recognise and approve follow-up comments automatically instead of placing them in a moderation queue. For users who register, we also store the personal information they provide in their profile. All users can view, edit or delete their personal information at any time (except their username). Administrators can also view and edit this information.</p>

      <h2>What rights you have over your data</h2>
      <p>If you have left data with us, you can request an export file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we delete all personal data we hold about you. This does not include data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal or security purposes.</p>

      <h2>Where we send your data</h2>
      <p>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this privacy policy or about the processing of your personal data, you can contact Resolve IT at <a href="mailto:contact@resolveit.nl">contact@resolveit.nl</a> or 0411 799 828.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
</content>
